
// The button layout feels imbalanced,
// too much strain on my right thumb
// Instead of just using the alpha buttons,
// I should also use the dpad for letter insertion
// with bl,br,sl + dpad,alpha = 24k combinations

// alpha:    aoet
// dpad:     dcsr
// BL+alpha: hlin
// BL+dpad:  gbwf
// BR+alpha: ypum
// BR+dpad:  qzvx
// SL+alpha: 1234
// SL+dpad:  5678
// SR+alpha: kj09
// SR+dpad:  <BS><DEL><ENTER><SPC>

// sr + dpad = arrow keys